            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Herculi In<lb break="no" n="2"/>victo sac<lb break="no" n="3"/>rum <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Ter<lb break="no" n="4"/>entius Bass<lb break="no" n="5"/>us |(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VI vi<lb break="no" n="6"/>ctricis et ve<lb break="no" n="7"/>xi<expan><ex>l</ex><abbr>latio</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>le</abbr><ex>gionis</ex></expan> e<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>usdem</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: bis Anfang der 120er Jahre; da die Legionsbeinamen pia fidelis fehlen, vermutlich vor 89 n. Chr.</p>
            </div>
